WEBVTT

00:01:31.100 --> 00:01:34.980
=Wonder Wall=

00:01:35.020 --> 00:01:37.910
=Episode 20=

00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:43.519
Before the ambulance arrived,

00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:45.760
you held me so tightly

00:01:47.640 --> 00:01:48.400
and kept telling me,

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:50.920
Nuo,

00:01:52.359 --> 00:01:52.959
it's okay.

00:01:54.719 --> 00:01:55.239
Don't be scared.

00:01:56.480 --> 00:01:56.959
It's all right.

00:01:58.959 --> 00:02:00.239
That warmth

00:02:01.879 --> 00:02:02.959
has always stayed with me.

00:02:07.799 --> 00:02:09.560
But somewhere along the way,

00:02:11.680 --> 00:02:12.599
that warmth

00:02:13.840 --> 00:02:14.879
slowly disappeared.

00:02:18.120 --> 00:02:19.280
And you never held me again.

00:02:21.240 --> 00:02:21.960
So I started to wonder,

00:02:23.360 --> 00:02:24.199
maybe if I could

00:02:24.199 --> 00:02:25.159
become what you wanted,

00:02:26.520 --> 00:02:27.840
then you would be that mother again.

00:02:29.639 --> 00:02:30.680
So I kept reaching for it.

00:02:34.080 --> 00:02:34.680
Even a casual

00:02:34.719 --> 00:02:36.000
word of praise from you

00:02:37.159 --> 00:02:38.120
could keep me happy for so long.

00:02:42.479 --> 00:02:43.520
But those moments

00:02:45.439 --> 00:02:46.240
never lasted.

00:02:54.120 --> 00:02:54.520
Mom.

00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:57.000
Because of this money,

00:02:57.759 --> 00:02:58.599
Dad lost his life.

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:00.960
And you paid the price too.

00:03:02.319 --> 00:03:03.159
How could I ever

00:03:03.240 --> 00:03:04.879
touch money bought with your lives?

00:03:06.599 --> 00:03:07.759
I don't hate you, really.

00:03:12.039 --> 00:03:13.000
I'm just afraid.

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:18.120
Afraid of becoming you.

00:03:20.479 --> 00:03:21.120
Blood

00:03:21.159 --> 00:03:22.199
is a strange thing.

00:03:23.159 --> 00:03:24.280
I can't deny it.

00:03:25.719 --> 00:03:26.599
Deep down,

00:03:27.479 --> 00:03:28.280
we are alike.

00:03:31.520 --> 00:03:32.479
That's what scares me.

00:03:34.360 --> 00:03:35.639
But the more I tried to run from you,

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:37.960
the more I became like you.

00:04:33.920 --> 00:04:37.639
There is a flash drive

00:04:39.040 --> 00:04:40.480
inside my fridge.

00:04:42.800 --> 00:04:43.639
It's important.

00:04:45.680 --> 00:04:46.680
It contains

00:04:48.519 --> 00:04:49.360
evidence

00:04:51.759 --> 00:04:52.839
of Li Jin's

00:04:54.560 --> 00:04:56.800
embezzlement six years ago.

00:04:58.560 --> 00:04:59.920
Hong Jinkui's death

00:05:02.279 --> 00:05:04.279
was tied to that flash drive.

00:05:06.600 --> 00:05:07.480
Li Jin

00:05:09.680 --> 00:05:10.319
was afraid

00:05:11.839 --> 00:05:13.879
the secret would get out.

00:05:15.800 --> 00:05:16.800
So she set up

00:05:19.439 --> 00:05:21.160
Hong Jinkui's murder.

00:05:22.931 --> 00:05:25.159
(Basement Fire Safety Plan)

00:05:39.839 --> 00:05:40.800
Every other week,

00:05:41.399 --> 00:05:42.120
the building has

00:05:42.120 --> 00:05:43.519
a fire equipment inspection.

00:05:44.959 --> 00:05:45.920
But the job

00:05:47.199 --> 00:05:48.600
is handled by an outside contractor.

00:05:49.560 --> 00:05:51.000
Slip in with their crew.

00:05:58.560 --> 00:06:00.480
Drive them where they need to go.

00:06:03.120 --> 00:06:04.319
What kind of dump is this?

00:06:04.839 --> 00:06:05.800
There is not even a parking spot.

00:06:36.279 --> 00:06:37.519
The fire elevator lobby at Lanhai

00:06:37.560 --> 00:06:38.399
has no cameras.

00:06:39.279 --> 00:06:40.600
Wait there for my call.

00:06:56.600 --> 00:06:57.279
Do it.

00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:05.959
The smoke detector will trigger

00:07:05.959 --> 00:07:07.879
the pre-action fire system.

00:07:08.759 --> 00:07:10.439
The pipes will vent and build pressure.

00:07:10.920 --> 00:07:12.360
The solenoid valve will open.

00:07:13.279 --> 00:07:14.160
Then...

00:07:22.680 --> 00:07:23.480
He is a rat.

00:07:24.120 --> 00:07:25.920
He keeps his stash in his nest.

00:07:26.519 --> 00:07:27.680
After you leave Lanhai,

00:07:27.879 --> 00:07:29.360
go to his place
and find the flash drive.

00:07:48.319 --> 00:07:48.759
Recently, Li,

00:07:48.959 --> 00:07:51.360
(Li is under investigation.)
former engineering design director

00:07:51.399 --> 00:07:52.199
of Luzhou Shengli Group, was arrested.

00:07:52.560 --> 00:07:53.879
The case has caused a major stir.

00:07:54.279 --> 00:07:55.600
It exposed

00:07:55.639 --> 00:07:56.879
a complex network of illicit deals,

00:07:57.319 --> 00:07:59.800
damaging fair market competition

00:08:00.120 --> 00:08:01.439
and public trust in government.

00:08:02.399 --> 00:08:05.000
From 2008 to 2017,

00:08:05.319 --> 00:08:07.759
several companies used Li's connections

00:08:07.920 --> 00:08:09.800
to obtain government subsidies by fraud

00:08:09.800 --> 00:08:10.600
for high-tech industries,

00:08:11.160 --> 00:08:12.600
win government-funded projects,

00:08:12.879 --> 00:08:14.079
and pay bribes to Li.

00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:15.759
The total exceeded 70 million yuan.

00:08:16.519 --> 00:08:18.079
Wang,
formerly of the Municipal Development

00:08:18.120 --> 00:08:20.439
and Reform Commission, aided them.

00:08:20.800 --> 00:08:22.439
During that period, he accepted bribes

00:08:22.519 --> 00:08:24.319
totaling over 15 million yuan.

00:08:24.319 --> 00:08:25.160
Thank you.

00:08:25.680 --> 00:08:26.279
For what?

00:08:27.160 --> 00:08:28.279
Without you,

00:08:29.279 --> 00:08:32.279
I might be the one on the news now.

00:08:32.279 --> 00:08:34.120
We will investigate the corruption,

00:08:34.200 --> 00:08:35.039
show no leniency,

00:08:35.159 --> 00:08:36.639
restore clean governance,

00:08:36.960 --> 00:08:38.200
and root out corruption completely.

00:08:39.000 --> 00:08:40.679
Wenwen's grades have been slipping.

00:08:40.759 --> 00:08:41.759
She is fine in her other subjects,

00:08:41.799 --> 00:08:42.879
but math is really a problem.

00:08:43.000 --> 00:08:43.960
She is not even passing.

00:08:45.279 --> 00:08:46.679
She is starting middle school soon.

00:08:47.080 --> 00:08:48.159
We need to get her a tutor.

00:08:58.080 --> 00:09:00.519
Let Wenwen go to public school.

00:09:01.879 --> 00:09:03.120
I think it's a good choice.

00:09:08.080 --> 00:09:08.600
Agreed.

00:09:11.440 --> 00:09:12.320
Great.

00:09:13.960 --> 00:09:14.879
Then let's

00:09:16.399 --> 00:09:17.600
get a good night's sleep.

00:09:18.919 --> 00:09:19.360
Good night.

00:09:25.200 --> 00:09:26.600
About Unit 505,

00:09:28.799 --> 00:09:29.679
I have thought it over.

00:09:31.639 --> 00:09:32.240
We should sell

00:09:32.279 --> 00:09:33.600
the place as soon as possible.

00:09:34.639 --> 00:09:36.399
The 1.02 million owed to Hong Jinkui

00:09:36.879 --> 00:09:37.639
should be paid back.

00:09:38.759 --> 00:09:40.279
He may be gone,

00:09:41.200 --> 00:09:42.799
but his mother is still alive.

00:09:43.559 --> 00:09:44.279
What do you think?

00:09:45.879 --> 00:09:47.200
Agreed.

00:09:48.519 --> 00:09:49.440
You are a good person.

00:09:54.360 --> 00:09:55.240
Then let's

00:09:56.240 --> 00:09:57.279
get a good night's sleep.

00:09:58.399 --> 00:09:58.960
Good night.

00:10:08.440 --> 00:10:09.000
Yu Ming.

00:10:13.120 --> 00:10:13.799
Nothing.

00:10:18.960 --> 00:10:20.039
I love you too.

00:10:36.840 --> 00:10:37.320
Dad.

00:10:38.600 --> 00:10:39.279
I'm sorry.

00:10:40.879 --> 00:10:41.919
I stayed away for so long.

00:10:44.399 --> 00:10:45.559
I kept thinking

00:10:46.279 --> 00:10:47.360
that if I didn't come,

00:10:48.039 --> 00:10:49.080
you would still be here.

00:10:50.879 --> 00:10:51.600
Don't worry.

00:10:52.600 --> 00:10:54.919
(Chen Liyang)
I had been doing okay these years.

00:10:56.440 --> 00:10:57.200
I'm healthy.

00:10:58.720 --> 00:10:59.559
And my life is peaceful.

00:11:02.639 --> 00:11:03.799
After Mom got out,

00:11:04.080 --> 00:11:05.320
she disturbed the peace.

00:11:06.840 --> 00:11:07.960
So much happened.

00:11:10.519 --> 00:11:11.720
Now she's behind bars again.

00:11:13.639 --> 00:11:14.399
I thought I could

00:11:14.399 --> 00:11:15.480
find that peace again.

00:11:17.759 --> 00:11:18.440
But I couldn't.

00:11:20.639 --> 00:11:21.639
So many feelings

00:11:23.080 --> 00:11:24.000
are blurred now.

00:11:26.799 --> 00:11:28.519
Life just feels empty.

00:11:33.720 --> 00:11:35.279
No one tells me what to do.

00:11:40.919 --> 00:11:41.919
For a while,

00:11:44.559 --> 00:11:45.320
I kept hoping

00:11:45.360 --> 00:11:46.159
someone would save me.

00:11:47.320 --> 00:11:48.240
Or just stay with me.

00:11:49.960 --> 00:11:50.720
Anything.

00:11:55.919 --> 00:11:57.120
But that's not how it works, Dad.

00:12:01.600 --> 00:12:02.559
No one can save me.

00:12:07.080 --> 00:12:07.919
You were right.

00:12:09.159 --> 00:12:10.080
The road ahead

00:12:12.039 --> 00:12:12.960
is mine to walk.

00:12:14.679 --> 00:12:16.320
Even if I don't know what is right,

00:12:18.279 --> 00:12:19.440
I have to find it myself.

00:12:34.879 --> 00:12:35.480
I'm leaving.

00:12:36.360 --> 00:12:36.840
Let's go.

00:12:39.360 --> 00:12:40.000
Hop on.

00:12:45.799 --> 00:12:46.720
I'm leaving this place.

00:12:47.399 --> 00:12:48.120
To Hanover.

00:12:49.679 --> 00:12:51.120
Hanover?

00:12:52.279 --> 00:12:53.120
Europe, right?

00:12:53.840 --> 00:12:55.039
I have never been there.

00:12:55.159 --> 00:12:56.399
But I heard it's fun.

00:12:56.759 --> 00:12:57.200
You know,

00:12:57.399 --> 00:12:58.519
I have always had this dream.

00:12:58.519 --> 00:12:59.279
To ride this moto

00:12:59.279 --> 00:13:00.919
all the way across Eurasia.

00:13:01.080 --> 00:13:01.879
I could take you

00:13:01.879 --> 00:13:02.879
to Hanover on my it.

00:13:02.879 --> 00:13:03.480
Not just Hanover.

00:13:03.720 --> 00:13:04.759
Other cities

00:13:04.759 --> 00:13:05.519
in Europe, too.

00:13:05.679 --> 00:13:06.519
We could eat good food,

00:13:06.600 --> 00:13:07.720
take beautiful photos of you,

00:13:07.759 --> 00:13:08.480
and

00:13:08.720 --> 00:13:09.440
visit many places.

00:13:09.519 --> 00:13:10.120
Ouyang.

00:13:10.120 --> 00:13:11.480
♪Sunlight falls through the curtains♪

00:13:11.879 --> 00:13:12.600
Some roads

00:13:13.480 --> 00:13:13.960
are meant

00:13:13.960 --> 00:13:14.799
to be walked alone.

00:13:18.279 --> 00:13:18.799
Thank you.

00:13:18.799 --> 00:13:19.720
♪A little secret♪

00:13:21.147 --> 00:13:23.880
♪Whenever we're together♪

00:13:24.496 --> 00:13:27.056
♪It's the perfect time♪

00:13:27.460 --> 00:13:29.520
♪A little understanding♪

00:13:30.840 --> 00:13:31.840
When will you come back?

00:13:33.679 --> 00:13:35.159
When I figure things out.

00:13:35.159 --> 00:13:35.880
♪When I look into your eyes♪

00:13:36.236 --> 00:13:37.360
♪I see the stars shining♪

00:13:37.360 --> 00:13:38.799
Call me when you miss me.

00:13:39.639 --> 00:13:41.080
My number won't change.

00:13:41.080 --> 00:13:42.600
♪Listening to your heartbeat♪

00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:45.000
♪Such a special rhythm♪

00:13:46.128 --> 00:13:48.120
♪I'm falling for you♪

00:13:49.718 --> 00:13:54.960
♪Now baby I love you♪

00:13:57.399 --> 00:13:58.759
Wenwen, wait for me.

00:13:59.240 --> 00:14:00.159
Wenwen, wait.

00:14:02.066 --> 00:14:03.720
♪Every second♪

00:14:04.360 --> 00:14:07.000
♪Every minute, every day♪

00:14:07.000 --> 00:14:08.840
♪I want to be by your side♪

00:14:08.840 --> 00:14:13.520
♪The moments that steal my heart♪

00:14:13.520 --> 00:14:16.840
(First Place)

00:14:20.639 --> 00:14:21.200
Who is that?

00:14:21.440 --> 00:14:22.120
That's my dad.

00:14:22.960 --> 00:14:23.559
Your dad?

00:14:24.720 --> 00:14:25.919
Your dad doesn't look like that.

00:14:26.440 --> 00:14:27.279
What do you know?

00:14:27.919 --> 00:14:29.120
I have two dads.

00:14:29.120 --> 00:14:30.200
♪Are the ones we share♪

00:14:30.800 --> 00:14:33.400
♪Another perfect day♪

00:14:33.400 --> 00:14:35.640
♪Rain or shine♪

00:14:36.360 --> 00:14:38.860
♪as long as I'm with you♪

00:14:41.840 --> 00:14:43.840
Are you all right?

00:14:45.279 --> 00:14:46.399
No.

00:14:46.440 --> 00:14:48.519
She thinks I'm peeling it too slowly.

00:14:48.559 --> 00:14:50.279
I just started.

00:14:52.200 --> 00:14:54.120
Don't move. Stay still.

00:14:58.960 --> 00:15:02.000
And I'm not as good as my brother.

00:15:02.000 --> 00:15:04.519
I'm disobedient and restless.

00:15:04.600 --> 00:15:06.840
My brother was always the perfect one.

00:15:07.600 --> 00:15:08.960
Even when we were kids,

00:15:09.159 --> 00:15:10.879
you always hit me, never my brother.

00:15:10.879 --> 00:15:11.399
My butt

00:15:11.399 --> 00:15:13.440
grew an extra cheek from the spankings.

00:15:14.919 --> 00:15:15.919
Relax. He's joking.

00:15:16.360 --> 00:15:16.919
Just kidding.

00:15:16.919 --> 00:15:19.759
She just took it the wrong way.

00:15:21.279 --> 00:15:24.159
Your blood pressure is way too high.

00:15:26.120 --> 00:15:27.679
She meant she's fine.

00:15:30.159 --> 00:15:31.039
Here. Take it.

00:15:35.519 --> 00:15:37.679
She is saying I never knew how to save.

00:15:37.759 --> 00:15:38.559
Never did?

00:15:38.600 --> 00:15:39.200
Right.

00:15:41.679 --> 00:15:42.559
If she hadn't helped me

00:15:42.559 --> 00:15:44.039
pay back Qian Weijie's 37,000,

00:15:44.039 --> 00:15:45.440
I could never have managed it.

00:15:46.559 --> 00:15:47.559
Right. Exactly.

00:15:47.799 --> 00:15:49.679
That was when

00:15:49.960 --> 00:15:51.440
I finally realized something.

00:15:52.639 --> 00:15:54.039
You do love me.

00:15:58.679 --> 00:15:59.840
Too sour.

00:16:08.639 --> 00:16:10.399
I know this place has a death in it.

00:16:10.600 --> 00:16:12.600
He was hanging right here, right?

00:16:13.120 --> 00:16:14.120
I heard

00:16:14.200 --> 00:16:14.759
he was up there

00:16:14.759 --> 00:16:16.879
for days before anyone found him.

00:16:16.919 --> 00:16:18.039
By the time the coroner came,

00:16:18.080 --> 00:16:19.399
the body was all swollen.

00:16:19.600 --> 00:16:20.720
The moment the coroner stepped in,

00:16:20.840 --> 00:16:21.840
there was this loud thud.

00:16:21.960 --> 00:16:23.320
The head and the neck

00:16:23.440 --> 00:16:24.399
just came apart.

00:16:24.519 --> 00:16:25.200
And the head

00:16:25.559 --> 00:16:27.279
was still hanging from this light.

00:16:27.559 --> 00:16:28.840
Did you hear that

00:16:29.039 --> 00:16:30.879
from the lady next door?

00:16:31.679 --> 00:16:32.559
What lady?

00:16:33.000 --> 00:16:34.399
That is my second sister.

00:16:35.159 --> 00:16:36.399
About the price,

00:16:36.559 --> 00:16:37.879
we can still talk.

00:16:38.759 --> 00:16:40.159
What was the price again?

00:16:40.559 --> 00:16:41.240
4.5 Million.

00:16:42.480 --> 00:16:43.399
That was the agent's price.

00:16:43.480 --> 00:16:44.000
Deal.

00:16:44.679 --> 00:16:45.759
Ever heard of a born jinx?

00:16:45.919 --> 00:16:46.399
That's me.

00:16:46.480 --> 00:16:47.120
I'm a lone jinx.

00:16:47.200 --> 00:16:48.120
Born too tough for fate.

00:16:48.240 --> 00:16:49.360
I outjinx everyone.

00:16:49.600 --> 00:16:50.519
The worse it gets for others,

00:16:50.639 --> 00:16:51.559
the better it gets for me.

00:16:51.679 --> 00:16:52.879
A fortune teller once told me

00:16:53.279 --> 00:16:55.080
my fate lacks misfortune.

00:16:55.480 --> 00:16:56.039
I need that.

00:16:56.480 --> 00:16:58.240
Bad luck

00:16:58.320 --> 00:16:58.799
does not exist

00:16:58.799 --> 00:16:59.919
when it comes to me.

00:17:00.120 --> 00:17:01.279
In my eyes,

00:17:01.399 --> 00:17:02.840
bad luck

00:17:02.879 --> 00:17:03.399
is the best.

00:17:03.919 --> 00:17:05.640
When everything goes my way,

00:17:05.720 --> 00:17:06.599
life gets boring.

00:17:06.960 --> 00:17:07.799
And when life gets boring,

00:17:07.880 --> 00:17:08.960
it starts to feel meaningless.

00:17:09.319 --> 00:17:09.720
So,

00:17:09.799 --> 00:17:11.559
I'm looking for the meaning of life.

00:17:11.640 --> 00:17:13.279
Everything has a purpose.

00:17:13.480 --> 00:17:14.440
So why should someone like me

00:17:14.519 --> 00:17:15.720
not have one?

00:17:17.000 --> 00:17:17.720
How much is the deposit?

00:17:18.000 --> 00:17:18.599
Five percent.

00:17:18.799 --> 00:17:19.759
Five percent of the full price.

00:17:19.839 --> 00:17:20.440
A little over 200 thousand.

00:17:20.759 --> 00:17:21.559
225 thousand.

00:17:21.599 --> 00:17:22.799
Round it up to 300 thousand.

00:17:23.519 --> 00:17:24.400
Your Alipay is linked to

00:17:24.480 --> 00:17:25.400
your phone number, right?

00:17:26.200 --> 00:17:26.799
Yes,

00:17:26.880 --> 00:17:28.279
but we didn't bring the contract today.

00:17:28.559 --> 00:17:30.119
I can go get it. It won't take long.

00:17:30.200 --> 00:17:31.039
I can be right back.

00:17:31.839 --> 00:17:33.000
I should have brought it.

00:17:33.000 --> 00:17:34.079
I didn't think we would actually...

00:17:34.319 --> 00:17:35.039
Your message.

00:17:35.519 --> 00:17:36.279
Well...

00:17:37.240 --> 00:17:38.559
I hate

00:17:38.599 --> 00:17:39.680
putting people to trouble.

00:17:40.799 --> 00:17:41.720
Today is...

00:17:42.119 --> 00:17:42.799
Friday.

00:17:43.000 --> 00:17:43.279
Right.

00:17:43.440 --> 00:17:44.160
Then we sign on Monday.

00:17:44.400 --> 00:17:45.599
I like to make decisions fast.

00:17:46.839 --> 00:17:47.720
People who do big things

00:17:47.799 --> 00:17:48.799
make decisions fast.

00:17:48.880 --> 00:17:49.519
Exactly.

00:17:50.799 --> 00:17:51.920
